TI  - Effect of oral calcitriol pulse therapy on the lipid, calcium, and glucose homeostasis of hemodialysis-patients: Its safety in a combination with oral calcium carbonate
T2  - JOURNAL OF RENAL NUTRITION
LA  - English
KW  - CHRONIC-RENAL-FAILURE
KW  - HYPERPARATHYROIDISM
KW  - DIALYSIS
KW  - UREMIA
KW  - OSTEODYSTROPHY
