TI  - Effects of prelay 6/85-strain Mycoplasma gallisepticum inoculation alone or in conjunction with the inoculation of F-strain Mycoplasma gallisepticum during lay on the blood characteristics of commercial egg-laying hens
T2  - POULTRY SCIENCE
LA  - English
