TI  - Effect of MCI-196 on serum phosphate and cholesterol levels in haemodialysis patients with hyperphosphataemia: a double-blind, randomized, placebo-controlled study
T2  - NEPHROLOGY DIALYSIS TRANSPLANTATION
LA  - English
KW  - calcium
