TI  - Effect of recombinant human erythropoietin on insulin, amino acid, and lipid metabolism in uremia
T2  - JOURNAL OF PEDIATRICS
LA  - English
KW  - THALASSEMIA MAJOR
KW  - GLUCOSE-INTOLERANCE
