TI  - ORGAN-SPECIFIC EFFECTS OF TIRATRICOL - A THYROID-HORMONE ANALOG WITH HEPATIC, NOT PITUITARY, SUPERAGONIST EFFECTS
T2  - JOURNAL OF CLINICAL ENDOCRINOLOGY & METABOLISM
LA  - English
