TI  - A structural equation model for assessment of links between changes in serum triglycerides, -urate, and -glucose and changes in serum Calcium, -magnesium and -phosphate in Type 2 diabetes and non-diabetes metabolism
T2  - CARDIOVASCULAR DIABETOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - URIC-ACID
