TI  - Evaluation of the impacts of nutritional support in maintenance Hemodialysis patients using anthropometric measurements, biochemical parameters, and the modified quantitative subjective global assessment (MQSGA)
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF CLINICAL AND EXPERIMENTAL MEDICINE
LA  - English
