TI  - Carotid atherosclerosis is a predictor of coronary calcification in chronic haemodialysis patients
T2  - NEPHROLOGY DIALYSIS TRANSPLANTATION
LA  - English
KW  - atherosclerosis
KW  - B-mode Doppler ultrasonography
KW  - electron beam computed tomography
