TI  - Coronary Atherosclerosis in Masters Athletes: Mechanisms and Implications for Cardiovascular Disease Risk
T2  - CURRENT TREATMENT OPTIONS IN CARDIOVASCULAR MEDICINE
LA  - English
KW  - Coronary artery disease
KW  - Masters athletes
KW  - Cholesterol
