TI  - The GLUT-1 XbaI gene polymorphism is associated with vascular calcifications in nondiabetic uremic patients
T2  - NEPHRON CLINICAL PRACTICE
LA  - English
KW  - vascular calcifications
KW  - GLUT-1 gene polymorphism
KW  - dialysis
