TI  - Feasibility study of colestipol as an oral phosphate binder in hemodialysis patients
T2  - NEPHROLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - haemodialysis
KW  - phosphate
KW  - phosphate binder
KW  - CORONARY-ARTERY CALCIFICATION
