TI  - Ameliorative potential of Tephrosia purpurea extract against arsenic induced toxicity in wistar rats
T2  - VETERINARY WORLD
LA  - English
KW  - arsenic
KW  - haematology
KW  - rats
KW  - serum bio-markers
