TI  - The incidence and characteristics of some paraneoplastic syndromes of hepatocellular carcinoma in Nigerian patients
T2  - EUROPEAN JOURNAL OF GASTROENTEROLOGY & HEPATOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - erythrocytosis
KW  - haematocrit
