TI  - Osmoregrulatory action of 17β-estradiol in the gilthead sea bream Sparus auratus
T2  - JOURNAL OF EXPERIMENTAL ZOOLOGY PART A-ECOLOGICAL AND INTEGRATIVE PHYSIOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - SALMON SALMO-SALAR
