TI  - Multinational observational study on clinical practices and therapeutic management of mineral and bone disorders in patients with chronic kidney disease stages 4, 5, and 5D: The OCEANOS study
T2  - SAUDI JOURNAL OF KIDNEY DISEASES AND TRANSPLANTATION
LA  - English
KW  - PARATHYROID-HORMONE CONTROL
