TI  - Oral Calcium Supplements Do Not Affect the Progression of Aortic Valve Calcification or Coronary Artery Calcification
T2  - JOURNAL OF THE AMERICAN BOARD OF FAMILY MEDICINE
LA  - English
KW  - LOW-DENSITY-LIPOPROTEIN
