TI  - Calcium Blood Level Elevation After Atorvastatin Initiation in a Patient With Hyperparathyroidism
T2  - CUREUS JOURNAL OF MEDICAL SCIENCE
LA  - English
KW  - drug -related adverse event
KW  - atorvastatin
KW  - prevention in primary care
