TI  - A new heterozygous mutation (D196N) in the Gs alpha gene as a cause for pseudohypoparathyroidism type IA in a boy who had gallstones
T2  - JOURNAL OF PEDIATRIC ENDOCRINOLOGY & METABOLISM
LA  - English
KW  - children
KW  - cholelithiasis
